{"url": "http://www.bbc.com/news/election-us-2016-37987306?ocid=socialflow_twitter", "text": "A fabricated news story claiming Hollywood actor Denzel Washington had praised US President-elect Donald Trump is being shared widely on Facebook.\n\nThe post from Facebook page American News has been shared more than 22,000 times since Monday.\n\nIt claims Mr Washington praised Mr Trump, saying: \"We need more and more jobs.\n\n\"He has hired more employees, more people, than anyone I know in the world.\"\n\nThe story also claims Mr Washington called President Barack Obama \"anti-Christian\".\n\nMr Washington's publicist Alan Nierob, external told BBC News: \"The story is 100% complete fabrication.\"", "images": ["https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/464/mcs/media/images/75306000/jpg/_75306515_line976.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/1060D/production/_92458076_hi036303238.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/FD74/production/_92448846_hi014044278.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/385/cpsprodpb/51f3/live/8bf57430-67c6-11f0-89ea-4d6f9851f623.png", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/385/cpsprodpb/07d9/live/077f2a60-6867-11f0-8dbd-f3d32ebd3327.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/385/cpsprodpb/589d/live/66ad7280-4562-11f0-82d5-89ce01115edf.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/385/cpsprodpb/d1bd/live/a77d6a80-681d-11f0-af20-030418be2ca5.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/385/cpsprodpb/4046/live/0b02ee00-5e63-11f0-b5c5-012c5796682d.png", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/385/cpsprodpb/544c/live/02f5b0d0-684a-11f0-8ac6-27b0e10b383d.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/07c7/live/07f6f270-6867-11f0-8dbd-f3d32ebd3327.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/4231/live/cc4a4730-5e2b-11f0-960d-e9f1088a89fe.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/385/cpsprodpb/172c/live/97cbded0-67d9-11f0-af20-030418be2ca5.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard